ack provenance through to the synth. (~3h) → deps: T-001\n-- **T-037** [T1] Build a deterministic replay harness that reproduces any past performance from (score, composition_seed, interpretation_seed, delta_track). (~3h) → deps: T-001\n+- **T-024** [T1] Define `SampleRecord` dataclass with sample-id, path, source, character tags, pitch, duration, captured-at, arc context, RMS, peak, transient density. (~3h) → deps: T-001\n+- **T-025** [T1] Define controlled `CHARACTER_TAGS` vocabulary (warm, metallic, wind, pulse, voice, mechanical, water, sustained, transient, percussive, harmonic, noisy). (~3h) → deps: T-001\n+- **T-026** [T1] Implement `SampleLibrary` on-disk store backed by `index.sqlite` with tag/source/pitch/mood-range queries. (~3h) → deps: T-001\n+- **T-027** [T1] Define on-disk directory layout under `/home/user/cypherclaw-data/samples/` with `library/`, `self/`, `room/`, `contact/`, `theramini/`, `keyboard/` subdirs and `index.sqlite`. (~3h) → deps: T-001\n+- **T-028** [T1] Implement `SampleSelector` mood/mode/arc-aware picker with deterministic seed-based selection within match set. (~3h) → deps: T-001\n+- **T-029** [T1] Add `sw_sampler` to `SIGNATURE_VOICES` quintet in `artist_identity.py` and update `VOICE_ROLES` so a `\"sampler\"` role maps to `\"sw_sampler\"`. (~3h) → deps: T-001\n+- **T-030** [T1] Add `sampler_density` field (0.0–1.0) to `ArtistMode` with mode-specific values: solitary 0.7, companion 0.25, working_ambience 0.10, evening_reflection 0.65, storm 0.45. (~3h) → deps: T-001\n+- **T-031** [T1] Register `voice_sampler` character in `character_registry.py` with `voice.synth = \"sw_sampler\"`, `voice.role = \"sampler\"`, default register, and per-mode gain overrides. (~3h) → deps: T-001\n+- **T-032** [T1] Implement `sw_sampler.scd` granular SynthDef with bufnum, grain-size, density, position-scrub, pitch-transpose, attack/release envelope, and effects-bus send. (~3h) → deps: T-001\n \n *Subtotal: ~27 hours*\n \n@@ -80,18 +75,16 @@ Sprints are