The helper follows local style and depends on existing `harmonic_planner` primitives used elsewhere, so it is consistent with SenseWeave harmonic conventions. Test placement and naming align with current module-level test patterns.

## Security
No security-sensitive operations are introduced. Input handling defaults/munges numeric fields defensively and does not read/write external resources.

